  <lyrics>[V1]
 Qhuyapfayasitay Dios Awqui.
 Take chuymaw mayissma
 Walja yanfanacaraquiwa,
 Nayatac wal sartasqui.
 
[C] 
 Dios Tatay jumaw nayan
 Arjjatirejjátajja,
 Ucat take chuymajjamp
 Jumar jac'achasinsma.
 
[V2]
 Familiajjas, amigojjasa,
 üñisipjjetuw, Tatay,
 Nayan juman cheka thaquimar
 Cutiquipstatajjáta.
 
[V3]
 Tatay, juc'amp jan walinacas
 Nayataquejj sartascpan,
 Chekpach juman ch'amamampejja
 Tucuycam sayfascaqufw.
 
</lyrics></song>